      <scopecontent>
         <head>Scope and Content Information</head>
         <p>Accounts of the general mercantile business of Christopher
         Tompkins of Mathews County, Virginia. Names in the accounts
         include William Bassett, James Brown, James Chewning, William
         Evans, Josiah Foster, John Green, Robert Hall, Richard Hunley,
         John Plummer, William H. Pruden, Thomas Sank, and James
         Saunders.</p>
      </scopecontent>
